Package: crew
Title: Components to Extend 'rrq' Workers
Description: The 'rrq' package leverages Redis, a state-of-the-art
  transactional in-memory database, to provide a powerful task queue for R.
  With interprocess communication, automatic down-scaling, and error handling,
  'rrq' orchestrates tasks at scale.
  The 'crew' package extends 'rrq' with components to deploy workers
  to a variety of distributed computing environments.
  With its unifying interface to multiple high-performance
  computing platforms, 'crew' resembles packages
  'clustermq' (2019, <doi:10.1093/bioinformatics/btz284>),
  'future' (2021, <doi:10.32614/RJ-2021-048>),
  and 'batchtools' (2017, <doi:10.21105/joss.00135>).
